WEBVTT

01:40.640 --> 01:45.940
[SPEED AND LOVE]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.860
[Episode 20]

01:52.720 --> 01:53.720
Gelas.

01:55.650 --> 01:57.039
Tuang sendiri.

01:58.229 --> 02:00.480
Paman, kelak semuanya akan lancar.

02:00.500 --> 02:02.290
Bagaimana langkah kita selanjutnya,
sejauh mana melangkah,

02:02.290 --> 02:03.170
