09:31.170 --> 09:32.570
Harus segera dioperasi.

09:34.290 --> 09:34.840
Ini...

09:35.080 --> 09:36.720
Dokter, apa maksud Anda?

09:37.680 --> 09:38.960
Penyempitan kardiovaskular

09:38.960 --> 09:41.410
